text: The Red Sea Fleet Command or officially Western Fleet (WF), also called " West Coast Fleet ", is a regional naval fleet and one of the two main formations of the Saudi Arabian Navy, with headquarters at Royal Naval Base at Jeddah, Western Province, that is the HQ and home port of the west sea fleet command of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. ==See also== * Eastern Fleet (Saudi Arabia) ==References== ==External links== * Fleet Category:Red Sea Category:Naval warfare Category:Naval fleets Category:Military units and formations established in 1800 Category:Military units and formations of Saudi Arabia
title: Western Fleet (Saudi Arabia)
